PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778415071
OL,3,CReform crush Labour to secure historic
OL,4,Cwins in Wakefield and Barnsley
OL,6,FMr Thomas, a newly elected councillor
OL,7,Ffor Alftofts and Whitwood, praised the
OL,8,Fefforts of his Reform colleagues.
OL,10,FHe said: "They have been out from
OL,11,Fmorning until night knocking on doors
OL,12,Fand talking to people, trying to
OL,13,Funderstand what the issues are and how
OL,14,Fpeople are feeling.
OL,16,F"Before this morning I thought we
OL,17,Fwould get between 40 and 45 seats, but
OL,18,Fwe are looking at upwards of 50."
OL,26,@rD@JOUxD@AOUzD@aO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
