CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778415071
OL,3,CReform crush Labour to secure historic
OL,4,Cwins in Wakefield and Barnsley
OL,6,FLabour's Sir Stephen Houghton, who has
OL,7,Fled Barnsley Council for 30 years,
OL,8,Fmaking him the second longest current
OL,9,Fserving council leader, was one of the
OL,10,Ffew to hold on. He retook his Cudworth
OL,11,Fseat by just 23 votes.
OL,13,FBut he was in no mood to celebrate.
OL,15,FSir Stephen said he was "emotional" to
OL,16,Flose Labour colleagues.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
