FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778415071
OL,3,CReform crush Labour to secure historic
OL,4,Cwins in Wakefield and Barnsley
OL,6,FHe added: "There are, across the
OL,7,Fcountry, left-behind places that feel
OL,8,Fthey have been ignored, feel their
OL,9,Feconomies have been ignored, feel they
OL,10,Fhave been ignored, that the
OL,11,Fgovernment's priorities lie with
OL,12,Fmigrants or other things, and it's
OL,13,Fcaused this kind of angst that we are
OL,14,Fseeing right across the country in
OL,15,Fworking class places, particularly
OL,16,Fwhite working class places."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
