PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778415071
OL,3,CReform crush Labour to secure historic
OL,4,Cwins in Wakefield and Barnsley
OL,6,FSir Stephen said: "At some point
OL,7,Fnational politicians are going to have
OL,8,Fto wake up because if they don't and
OL,9,Fcarry on the current direction it'll
OL,10,Fbe the same next year and the year
OL,11,Fafter and the year after. And the
OL,12,Fgenerals have to realise you don't
OL,13,Fwant any battles if you haven't got
OL,14,Fany troops left."
